{"tid":1722490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[血債不能票償]Sorry有人唔係淨係想票區選","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T11:20:10.000Z","uid":7270,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"294b6acdaa8ba38c6395bcb04003534ca1ab7c5c","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:21.000Z","msg":"中大既手足，首先多謝你地咁辛苦，守左咁多日。<br />\n但我覺得你地個叫價太低，只係要求區選順利進行。<br />\n<br />\n其實港共一早吹緊風叫人投票，佢恨不得可以用區選維穩。係無政制改變底下，區選變相係反映唔到民意，亦唔見得需要用咁多人死傷去換返來。<br />\n<br />\n但連登一定有人屌我分化撚，因為區選係神聖而不可侵犯的。<br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好岩岩打返起個勢又諗住血債票償好無？<br />\n唉。<br />\n<br />\n有人係想要真真正正既普選，但呢個po俾人拉沉我預左的了。<br />\n<br />\n頭先topic打錯，再開過。"},{"pid":"3370ad6e3ee97e52f5140d5054554d6b307129a7","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b5c1c7394229a1293f27988a35ad09c19d37686","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e6517732253672f87ba9d7d0f8f5c3fae361353","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:04:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e00fde35638b046fb969767724903adbfbc43761","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df75a77fada978f15b4f22b596d4f95ba76383da","tid":1722490,"uid":266548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:06:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"231cb332c6d2fec088ddb82422d1a5d585148c84","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10060f425f8823c7560c8d64248893c219973e15","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12e84811e930e09dfe446608cdb9390cf632bd40","tid":1722490,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02